<br>
After a while he messes it up and runs away to get 'help', of course he doesnt return and al'kabor apeared at the huge set of spires in DL (not the usualy TP ones). So Al'kabor is pretty annoyed we just summoned him when he didnt need help, and he then went on to say he has been researching the unknown and had discovered a new place called the nexus. We helped him close a huge rift that had opened in DL's and then he asked us too meet him at the normal wizard spires in DL's...<br>
<br>
We met al'kabor there and he gave us each a copy of his latest research. He told us to give to his apprentice, who conveniently spawned right by us. Hes the same guy who gives the ore of fusibility quest...we gave him our research and we recieved..<br>
<br>
Al'kabors prolyn of the nexus <br>
<br>
AC15 +50 hps +20 Mr effect :    <br>
Neck slot, lore, do drop, artifact etc.<br>
<br>
Al'kabor said that once he discovers more about the 'unknown' he would need our help, and the necklaces would grant us the ability to gate to the nexus. So...I asume when SOL goes live it will have right click nexus portal effect.<br>
<br>
Oh he gave us all titles too, which was 'of the nexus'....<br>
<br>
wish I had a log of this or some screenshots =/, was 3 am UK time when I did the quest hehe<br>
